import React from "react"; import "./DietaryIcon.css"; // Archivo CSS para estilos personalizados. // Rutas relativas a la carpeta de íconos const dietaryIcons = { // Restricciones Dietéticas vegetarian: "icons/vegetarian.png", // FET vegan: "icons/vegan.png", // FET pescatarian: "icons/contains_fish.png", // FET ketogenic: "icons/keto.png", // FET paleo: "icons/paleo.png", // FET primal: "icons/primal.png", // FET lowFODMAP: "icons/low-fodmap.png", whole30: "icons/whole30.png", highProtein: "icons/high-protein.png", lowCarb: "icons/low_carb.png", // FET lowFat: "icons/low_fat.png", // FET sugarConscious: "icons/sugar_conscious.png", // FET // Intolerancias y Alérgenos glutenFree: "icons/gluten_free.png", // FET dairyFree: "icons/dairy-free.png", eggFree: "icons/egg_free.png", // FET peanutFree: "icons/no_nuts.png", // FET treeNutFree: "icons/tree-nut-free.png", soyFree: "icons/soy_free.png", // FET fishFree: "icons/fish_free.png", // FET shellfishFree: "icons/shellfish-free.png", wheatFree: "icons/wheat_free.png", // FET sesameFree: "icons/sesame_free.png", // FET sulfiteFree: "icons/sulfit_free.png", // FET celeryFree: "icons/celery_free.png", // FET mustardFree: "icons/mustard_free.png", // FET lupinFree: "icons/lupin-free.png", molluskFree: "icons/mollusk-free.png", // Información Nutricional calories: "icons/calories.png", carbohydrates: "icons/carbohydrates.png", proteins: "icons/proteins.png", fats: "icons/fats.png", cholesterol: "icons/cholesterol.png", fiber: "icons/fiber.png", sugar: "icons/sugar.png", // Ícono genérico default: "icons/default.png", }; const DietaryIcon = ({ diet }) => { const icon = dietaryIcons[diet] || dietaryIcons.default; // Ícono por defecto si no se encuentra el especificado. return (
{diet}
); }; export default DietaryIcon;
